Package de.fuberlin.wiwiss.d2rq.jena

Class Summary
CachingGraphD2RQ A GraphD2RQ that caches the results of the most recently performed queries on an LRU basis.
D2RQQueryHandler An implementation of Jena's QueryHandler interface that answers BGP queries on behalf of a GraphD2RQ.
GraphD2RQ A D2RQ virtual read-only Jena graph backed by a non-RDF database.
ModelD2RQ A D2RQ read-only Jena model backed by a D2RQ-mapped non-RDF database.
